  "kind": "Definition",
  "title": "Pointwise Sum of Functions",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $X\\subseteq\\mathbb{R}$ and let $f,g:X\\to\\mathbb{R}$. The\npointwise sum $f+g:X\\to\\mathbb{R}$ is the function defined by\n\\[\n (f+g)(x)=f(x)+g(x)\n \\qquad (x\\in X).\n\\]",
